(7, 'Grand Day Submission', '	<div class=''font_8'' style=''font-size: 16px; color: white;''>Send your\n		Grand Day Submissions via this Form.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Simply put in\n		your name, your Grand Day gross profit, and the date that you had your\n		GRAND DAY.&nbsp; The Grand Day slide will be updated at the end of the\n		week (SUNDAY) and will run throughout the following Week.&nbsp;\n		Congraduations on your GRAND DAY!</div>\n	<br style=''clear: both;'' />\n\n', 1, 4, 0),
