(5, 5, 'Top Content', 'top_content', '	<img src=''/big-board/images/a69938_c34cfb92e4c147ada96c9479d17a46da.jpg''/>\n	<div class=''font_8'' style=''font-size: 16px; color: white;''>\n	<br/><br/>\n        We know your Nature Sleep sales have been great all year and are literally exploding right now with our nationwide business up several hundred percent. RSS and Nature Sleep teamed up this week to look at something to make them even better. A Thanksgiving promotion that includes your customers and let''s you work the national scope of the Mattress wholesaler who you help move excessive mattress inventory. RSS and Royal Heritage Sleep are running a national promotion where any consumer purchasing a Royal Heritage Nature Sleep mattress has the chance to win $300 cash back if they are selected. \n         <br/><br/>\n        RSS will be posting a Big-Board slide this week with all the details and a customer/dealer registration form. From Saturday the 21st through Saturday the 28th all Nature Sleep sales that have a contest-sales registration card filed out go into the drawing. There will be three prizes:\n         <br/><br/>\n        1) Dealer with the most registered sales automatic $200\n         <br/><br/>\n        2) Every sale with a customer registration card filled out goes into a drawing. The week after the contest we will draw one from the hat and that customer will get $300 Directly from Royal Heritage by Nature Sleep.\n         <br/><br/>\n        3) The dealer that sells the customer drawn gets $500.\n         <br/><br/>\n        So, if your Number 1 in sales, you will automatically get $200 plus have the most cards in the drawing as you get one for each sale. That means the number one dealer has the best chance to win a total of $700 and have a customer receive $300 directly from Royal Heritage Nature Sleep.\n        <br/><br/>\n	</div>\n'),
